text: Henry Mervyn may refer to: *Sir Henry Mervyn (died 1646), English MP for Hindon (UK Parliament constituency) * Henry Mervyn (died 1699), Irish MP for Augher (Parliament of Ireland constituency) and County Tyrone * Henry Mervyn (died 1748), Irish MP for Augher and County Tyrone (Parliament of Ireland constituency)
title: Henry Mervyn
